              <h3>Use Code Instantly!</h3>
              <p>If you haven't already downloaded a text editor - this is the time. For mac I suggest <a href="http://www.sublimetext.com">Sublime</a> and for windows <a href="http://notepad-plus-plus.org">Notepad++.</a> You should also know how file structures work on your machine. Create a new file in your text editor called index.html and paste this code:</p>
